    "diffSummary": "Added zca-rust as a pinned git dependency (rev 08698e1c, rustls TLS — no native bindings) plus tokio to src-tauri/Cargo.toml, and created the zalo/ layer (src-tauri/src/zalo/mod.rs) that wraps Zalo::new(None).login() and re-exports the API facade, Credentials, and ZaloError. lib.rs declares the module. An offline cargo test proves the wrapper rejects empty credentials via zca-rust validation without any network call. Forward-only layering (types→config→store→zalo→session→command) is preserved; nothing above zalo added yet.",
